{"tid":674362,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻燕子係門口築巢","createTime":"2018-05-22T15:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T10:04:41.000Z","uid":4384,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b891d57db79995c68c34fc4837f2877d6a9558b2","tid":674362,"uid":4384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/225318_6fd5d5a25d0b2b638977f4d803fbdaa2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F225318_6fd5d5a25d0b2b638977f4d803fbdaa2.JPG&h=6b72ae0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上兩個星期開始，每日有隻燕子企係紅外探測器上，覺得佢想係到築巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/225913_4b4d84dad683fdd4eee462312b4662a0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F225913_4b4d84dad683fdd4eee462312b4662a0.JPG&h=f784a509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是買左個巢放係對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由於近行人路，就算屙屎的話，都方便打理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/230515_ef34906de1fa69d7db1ec664d7a29ad4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F230515_ef34906de1fa69d7db1ec664d7a29ad4.JPG&h=adf9f275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人工巢放左成個星期，唔知睇唔到定唔鍾意個人工巢<br />\n一定要係探測器上面起巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/231038_79253eb2a1d455945bbc85ef9be3be45.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F231038_79253eb2a1d455945bbc85ef9be3be45.JPG&h=96a03e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日仲帶條女返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，大家有咩方法令佢地係搬去人工巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9331e5d57841a8a0beffc7a11e63b3e001f9e6bb","tid":674362,"uid":3302,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"有免費燕窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎去賣 好快儲到首期<br />\nfatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2634482933132662589e2094a8e82b139076e78b","tid":674362,"uid":184233,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"燕窩啊 本地香港燕窩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家陣本地真係好少 <br />\n葡萄樓主"},{"pid":"dd094b82915b11e3a09661c424f002ae153254f0","tid":674362,"uid":14062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想有燕子係我門前築巢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af0a188975fdf5b6de971ce98e330334cfd87f","tid":674362,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"樓主快啲買6合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭獎你中硬"},{"pid":"590fc2b2cd7f582bc34f511d87f96d96cf09dd17","tid":674362,"uid":60408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔自己去就唔好夾硬搬佢個巢啦<br />\n由得佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95444a7b8126a139f2b09e1af7cc840733b4a26b","tid":674362,"uid":